@baseURL = http://localhost:5050
@userId = 28
@sessionId = 30

### Create Session
POST {{baseURL}}/api/chat/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "title": "Test Chat"
}

### Send Message - Gửi câu hỏi
POST {{baseURL}}/api/chat/sessions/{{sessionId}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Chim cút cần ăn gì?"
}

### Get Messages - Xem tin nhắn
GET {{baseURL}}/api/chat/sessions/{{sessionId}}/messages
